main: ^I am THE famous Chef Gordo, and here I am waiting for a taxi like a commoner.
^Hey you, I hear you're running for mayor yes? Answer this, what is the name of the famously angry British chef who is also my business partner?

c-0: ^Not quite. You should learn your chefs before you become mayor.
c-1: ^As much as I believe he is the greatest chef in the world besides myself, you are wrong.
c-2: ^How correct you are! It's always good to have a mayor who knows their chefs. People don't believe me when I say we're business partners but it's true! Trust me! Anyway you have my vote.
